      <odd id="aspace_4deeaf8ad1dc96dd72c0d58ff97abac7">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 15-B (YRG 15-B), Records of specific Yale summer and special programs.</p>  
      </odd>
